{
  "stem": "23350.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Theresienstadt?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- in Oederan?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Oederan-- Oederan, we were a transport of 300.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were all girls, and they were from different nationalities, actually, because they were all already from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We came from Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some were from Czechoslovakia-- many.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some were from Hungary and from Poland, and some from Germany also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had in-- in Oederan, we had two doctors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were doctors who started before the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were, naturally.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they had no medicine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had none.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They couldn't do anything if somebody was ill.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we-- we had to work at the munition factory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But many a time, when there wasn't enough work for everybody, everybody was standing near the door.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They wanted to get out into the fresh air-- to do any work, as long as you could get out of this prison.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And on-- on some of these occasions, I-- I was taken where we-- we had to go and push a cart.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And Oederan is a very hilly village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was terribly difficult, because we were really already so starved, you know, from all this period of-- from coming from '42 till '44, and in Auschwitz, and in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was very, very hard-going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that was really cold there in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were in this very thin-- just in a-- in a-- in a dress.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We had no clothes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had no coat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had just a pair of shoes, which they had given us a pair of old shoes from-- from Auschwitz, which they-- the people-- and we went.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Often, we had to go in and clean up the places from these German women.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they would have a whole loaf of bread lying in the-- in the-- in the rubbish bin.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
